  "texts": [
    "By comparing sensor data with these reference points, any discrepancies can be identified and corrected, ensuring high measurement accuracy.Finally, Terrestrial Laser Scanning (TLS) is utilized to establish ground truth.",
    "As a variant of LiDAR, TLS swiftly scans and captures 3D data of the environment.",
    "Due to its extensive reach and high-resolution data, TLS-based ground truth serves as a benchmark for aligning individual scans.",
    "The alignment of these scans to the TLS-derived ground truth enables the determination of the robot's 6-DOF state, which then serves as the definitive reference for LiDAR odometry.",
    "Evaluation methodsIn the evaluation of LiDAR odometry, several quantitative metrics are pivotal for assessing the accuracy and effectiveness of algorithms."
